People used to have kids cause that’s what happened after sex or cause that’s just what everyone did. Starting with your  grandparents generation though people started making choices.  Your mother I choose to have you and hopefully others for the following 

1. We believe we are good people and want there to be more good people.
1. Children are the only real chance at immortality.
1. Children bring an unrelatable joy. 
1. Altruism is actually important.  
